<title>Declarations</title>

<para>
A declaration precedes an expression.
It binds one or more variables to values, or type variables to types, in that expression. 
Declarations follow the rules of <link xlink:href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lexical_scoping#Lexical_scoping">lexical scoping</link>.
</para>

<para>
Declarations introduce new abstractions, services, and types. 
</para>

